a</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">- = Guión</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">_ = Guión bajo</span></p>\n<p>Zapamtite da reč <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Guión</span> ima tačku iznad slova <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span>.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-warm-up-describing-people-at-work-basics","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-warm-up-describing-people-at-work-basics/task-12"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>. = BLANK</p>\n<p>@ = BLANK</p>\n<p>- = BLANK</p>\n<p>_ = BLANK</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"Punto","feedback":"<p>Ovo je naziv znaka za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">.</span> na španskom.</p>"},{"answer":"Arroba","feedback":"<p>Ovo je naziv znaka za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">@</span> na španskom.</p>"},{"answer":"Guión","feedback":"<p>Ovo je naziv znaka za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">-</span> na španskom. Zapamtite da napišete kružni znak na slovo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span>.</p>"},{"answer":"Guión bajo","feedback":"<p>Ovo je naziv znaka <span class=\"highlighted-text\">_</span> na španski. Zapamti da staviš kružni znak na slovo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span> prve reči.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-dining.png","characters":[{"character":"Camila","position":{"x":50,"y":18,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_warm_up_describing_people_at_work.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":31.55,"finishTimestamp":37.62},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Camila","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Camila","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.8,"dialogue":{"text":"Punto","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Camila","position":null,"opacity":null,"st